                        <interp inst="t18370612-name-1327" type="given" value="ROBERT"></interp>ROBERT ELSTON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable M</hi> 28.) I had information, and fol<lb></lb>lowed the prisoner—he dropped the bag and escaped—I am sure he is the man—I knew him before.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
