                        <interp inst="t18370612-name-1328" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN SIMS</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman M</hi> 164.) I took the prisoner on the Saturday evening, between twelve and one o'clock, from the description—he said he had not been in the neighbourhood, but had just come from Epsom races, and knew nothing of it.</p>
